data.description: Make this home in the heart of Denham Springs your own! This cozy, vintage cottage on a 1/2 acre lot with convenient access to Florida Blvd and I 12 has been completely updated and is now waiting for your finishing touches. The home features all new kitchen cabinets and countertops, appliances, flooring (no carpet), and bathroom fixtures, as well as new windows and metal roof installed in 2017. Outside metal storage has electricity and the backyard has plenty of potential to make your outdoor living space dreams a reality. Call or text today for a tour!
